{"tid":1306073,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國豬瘟問題影響香港","createTime":"2019-07-11T04:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T04:49:46.000Z","uid":29914,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a82f6a766599f6d7599b730c80e6dc855ffa2287","tid":1306073,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"無人留意活豬係香港價格上升問題。<br />\n<br />\n中國豬瘟終於影響香港啦。睇個勢會影響埋其他肉類， 甚至蔬果價格。到時中共一定賴香港人示威所以減少供應導致價格上升。文宣好重要。真相好重要。<br />\n<br />\n支爆近了。"},{"pid":"34f29c26b20f62843cd7e57ab0c6f35613e5ddab","tid":1306073,"uid":181675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"蝗禍咁耐又唔見有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcbd55ad543baeb144a1202532ce63c859286d3","tid":1306073,"uid":29914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34f29c26b20f62843cd7e57ab0c6f35613e5ddab","tid":1306073,"uid":181675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"蝗禍咁耐又唔見有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:49:46.000Z","msg":"如果你 呢幾年有上過去啲二三線城市你就知。 14 、15年仲好多人揸車， 舊年已經條街勁空虛。 冇咩車， 同埋當地生果越賣越貴。"}]}